  "prompt": "What are the top 5 headphones under Rs.1000 in India?",
  "response": "As of my last update in October 2023, here are five popular headphones under Rs. 1000 in India that are well-regarded for their performance, build quality, and value for money. Please check the latest prices and availability before making a purchase, as these can change.\n\n1. **Boat Bassheads 100**:\n   - Type: In-ear\n   - Features: 10mm drivers, good sound quality, tangle-free cable, and comfortable fit.\n   - Notes: Known for punchy bass and decent noise isolation.\n\n2. **Zebronics Zeb-Rush**:\n   - Type: Over-ear\n   - Features: Dual 3.5mm connectors, adjustable headband, soft ear cushions.\n   - Notes: Offers a comfortable fit for extended listening sessions.\n\n3. **Redgear Cloak Wired RGB Gaming Headphones**:\n   - Type: Over-ear\n   - Features: RGB lighting, decent sound quality, adjustable microphone.\n   - Notes: Good for both gaming and multimedia consumption.\n\n4. **Mi Basic Earphones**:\n   - Type: In-ear\n   - Features: Dual drivers for optimized sound, built-in microphone, and control button.\n   - Notes: Offers a balanced sound profile, making it suitable for various genres.\n\n5. **Kotion Each GS410**:\n   - Type: Over-ear gaming headphones\n   - Features: Noise isolation, comfortable padding, and adjustable headband.\n   - Notes: A good choice for gamers looking for budget-friendly options.\n\nMake sure to read recent reviews and check for user feedback to ensure that they meet your requirements!",
